<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Community Member Removal Notice</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .reason-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #fd5901;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FD5901 0%, #9306FF 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #fd5901;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://thecapitalhub.in/static/media/logo-white.c4e4dacf1f6283c93e11.png" alt="CapitalHub Logo" class="logo">
    
    <h2>Community Membership Termination Notice</h2>
    
    <p>Dear <%= memberName %>,</p>
    
    <p>We regret to inform you that your membership in the community "<span class="highlight"><%= communityName %></span>" has been terminated by the community administrator, <%= adminName %>.</p>
    
    <p>Reason for removal:</p>
    <div class="reason-box">
      <%= reason %>
    </div>
    
    <p>While we understand this may be disappointing, we encourage you to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Explore other communities that align with your interests</li>
      <li>Review our community guidelines for future participation</li>
      <li>Reach out to our support team if you have any questions</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="https://thecapitalhub.in/explore-communities" class="cta-button">
      Explore Other Communities
    </a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you believe this action was taken in error, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The CapitalHub Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 